long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A lightweight and open-source extension to open the currently open summoner on a different League of Legends stats website. For example, if you have a profile open on op.gg you can open it on u.gg, leagueofgraphs.com and others. 

Currently supported websites:
op.gg
u.gg
xdx.gg
LeagueOfGraphs.com
mobalytics.gg
deeplol.gg

Other websites can be added easily, if you want a website added please open a issue on the github page or create a pull request.

The extension is open-source and the source code can be found at: https://github.com/isak102/lol-teleport
